The reputation of Boeing’s Dreamliner took another blow when a passenger on one of the aircraft spotted fuel gushing from the wing as it taxied for take-off.

The Norwegian Airlines 787 was preparing to take off from Bangkok on a journey to Oslo on Sunday when passenger Ann Kristin Balto saw that fuel was leaking on to the runway.

She immediately alerted a stewardess and the flight was cancelled.

